{"position":1,"ar":"وَيَقُولُونَ","fr":"Et ils disent","en":"And they say","tr":"wayaqūlūna","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"مَتَىٰ","fr":"Quand","en":"When","tr":"matā","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"هَـٰذَا","fr":"(est) ceci","en":"(is) this","tr":"hādhā","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ٱلْوَعْدُ","fr":"promesse","en":"promise","tr":"l-waʿdu","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"إِن","fr":"si","en":"if","tr":"in","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"كُنتُمْ","fr":"vous êtes","en":"you are","tr":"kuntum","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","fr":"véridique","en":"truthful","tr":"ṣādiqīna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":26,"verseKey":"67:26","juz":29,"arabic":"قُلْ إِنَّمَا ٱلْعِلْمُ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ وَإِنَّمَآ أَنَا۠ نَذِيرٌ مُّبِينٌ","fr":"Dis : « Seul Allah en détient la Science, quant à moi, je ne suis là que pour avertir en toute clarté. »","en":"Say, \"The knowledge is only with Allāh, and I am only a clear warner.\"","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"قُلْ","fr":"Dis","en":"Say","tr":"qul","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"إِنَّمَا","fr":"Seulement","en":"Only","tr":"innamā","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"ٱلْعِلْمُ","fr":"la connaissance","en":"the knowledge","tr":"l-ʿil'mu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"عِندَ","fr":"(est) avec","en":"(is) with","tr":"ʿinda","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"ٱللَّهِ","fr":"Allah","en":"Allah","tr":"l-lahi","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"وَإِنَّمَآ","fr":"et seulement","en":"and only","tr":"wa-innamā","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"أَنَا۠","fr":"je suis","en":"I am","tr":"anā","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"نَذِيرٌۭ","fr":"un avertisseur","en":"a warner","tr":"nadhīrun","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"مُّبِينٌۭ","fr":"clair","en":"clear","tr":"mubīnun","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":27,"verseKey":"67:27","juz":29,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا رَأَوْهُ زُلْفَةً سِيٓـَٔتْ وُجُوهُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ وَقِيلَ هَـٰذَا ٱلَّذِى كُنتُم بِهِۦ تَدَّعُونَ","fr":"Lorsqu’ils l’auront vu de très près, les mécréants en auront le visage tout blême, et il leur sera dit : « Voici ce que vous appeliez (de vos vœux avec empressement) ! »","en":"But when they see it approaching, the faces of those who disbelieve will be distressed, and it will be said, \"This is that for which you used to call.\"","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"فَلَمَّا","fr":"Mais quand","en":"But when","tr":"falammā","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"رَأَوْهُ","fr":"ils (va) voir cela","en":"they (will) see it","tr":"ra-awhu","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"زُلْفَةًۭ","fr":"approchant","en":"approaching","tr":"zul'fatan","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"سِيٓـَٔتْ","fr":"(va être) affligé","en":"(will be) distressed","tr":"sīat","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"وُجُوهُ","fr":"(le) visages","en":"(the) faces","tr":"wujūhu","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"ٱلَّذِينَ","fr":"(de) ceux qui","en":"(of) those who","tr":"alladhīna","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"كَفَرُوا۟","fr":"a mécru","en":"disbelieved","tr":"kafarū","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"وَقِيلَ","fr":"et cela va être dit","en":"and it will be said","tr":"waqīla","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"هَـٰذَا","fr":"Ceci","en":"This","tr":"hādhā","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"ٱلَّذِى","fr":"(est) ce qui","en":"(is) that which","tr":"alladhī","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"كُنتُم","fr":"vous aviez l'habitude de","en":"you used to","tr":"kuntum","isWaqf":false},{"position":12,"ar":"بِهِۦ","fr":"pour cela","en":"for it","tr":"bihi","isWaqf":false},{"position":13,"ar":"تَدَّعُونَ","fr":"appeler","en":"call","tr":"taddaʿūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":28,"verseKey":"67:28","juz":29,"arabic":"قُلْ أَرَءَيْتُمْ إِنْ أَهْلَكَنِىَ ٱللَّهُ وَمَن مَّعِىَ أَوْ رَحِمَنَا فَمَن يُجِيرُ ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ مِنْ عَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ","fr":"Dis : « Méditez donc ceci : si Allah me fait périr ainsi que ceux qui sont avec moi, ou s’Il nous reçoit dans Sa miséricorde, qui mettra les mécréants à l’abri d’un supplice très douloureux ? »","en":"Say, [O Muḥamm