relied. And you will [come to] know who it is that is in clear error.\"","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"قُلْ","fr":"Dis","en":"Say","tr":"qul","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"هُوَ","fr":"Il","en":"He","tr":"huwa","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ","fr":"(est) le Tout-Miséricordieux","en":"(is) the Most Gracious","tr":"l-raḥmānu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ءَامَنَّا","fr":"nous croire","en":"we believe","tr":"āmannā","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"بِهِۦ","fr":"dans Lui","en":"in Him","tr":"bihi","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"وَعَلَيْهِ","fr":"et sur Lui","en":"and upon Him","tr":"waʿalayhi","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"تَوَكَّلْنَا ۖ","fr":"nous mettre (notre) dépôt","en":"we put (our) trust","tr":"tawakkalnā","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"فَسَتَعْلَمُونَ","fr":"Donc vous saurez","en":"So you will know","tr":"fasataʿlamūna","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"مَنْ","fr":"qui","en":"who","tr":"man","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"هُوَ","fr":"(est) cela","en":"(is) it","tr":"huwa","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"فِى","fr":"(que est) dans","en":"(that is) in","tr":"fī","isWaqf":false},{"position":12,"ar":"ضَلَـٰلٍۢ","fr":"égarement","en":"error","tr":"ḍalālin","isWaqf":false},{"position":13,"ar":"مُّبِينٍۢ","fr":"clair","en":"clear","tr":"mubīnin","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":30,"verseKey":"67:30","juz":29,"arabic":"قُلْ أَرَءَيْتُمْ إِنْ أَصْبَحَ مَآؤُكُمْ غَوْرًا فَمَن يَأْتِيكُم بِمَآءٍ مَّعِينٍۭ","fr":"Dis enfin : « Méditez encore ceci : si votre eau était aspirée bien loin dans les profondeurs de la terre, qui donc vous apporterait de l’eau qui coule de source ? »","en":"Say, \"Have you considered: if your water was to become sunken [into the earth], then who could bring you flowing water?\"","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"قُلْ","fr":"Dis","en":"Say","tr":"qul","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"أَرَءَيْتُمْ","fr":"As-tu vu","en":"Have you seen","tr":"ara-aytum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"إِنْ","fr":"si","en":"if","tr":"in","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"أَصْبَحَ","fr":"devient","en":"becomes","tr":"aṣbaḥa","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"مَآؤُكُمْ","fr":"votre eau","en":"your water","tr":"māukum","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"غَوْرًۭا","fr":"englouti","en":"sunken","tr":"ghawran","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"فَمَن","fr":"puis qui","en":"then who","tr":"faman","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"يَأْتِيكُم","fr":"pourrait apporter vous","en":"could bring you","tr":"yatīkum","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"بِمَآءٍۢ","fr":"eau","en":"water","tr":"bimāin","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"مَّعِينٍۭ","fr":"coulant","en":"flowing","tr":"maʿīnin","isWaqf":false}]}]